Place environment-specific secrets in this folder (they are gitignored).
The docker-compose.yml mounts this directory at /home/androidusr/config inside the container.

Expected files:
  - my-debug-keystore.jks   (debug keystore used to sign the rebuilt Espresso test APK;
                             must match the keystore used to sign app-debug.apk)

See config/espresso-build-config.example.json for a reference of the
espressoBuildConfig shape (signing + Compose/AndroidX deps). Omit
toolsVersions.gradle / androidGradlePlugin unless you have a reason to
override the driver's defaults. The live configuration is embedded directly in
AndroidDriverManager.java and does not need to be a file here.
